Changes since 7.0.0
    - Added setting to be able to use "Logitech Number Pad" which we cannot use in Mac OS X.
      Activate "Change KeyPad Key > Logitech Number Pad Hack".
    - Added the fade-out feature to StatusWindow.
      Set "[StatusWindow] FadeOut Duration" in "Key Repeat" tab to activate fade-out.
      (It's useful using "General > Continue displaying empty status message" together.)
    - Improve UI of checkForUpdate.
    - Fixed minor bugs.
    - Added about XXX kinds settings.
